{"tid":1373461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屠夫李鵬遺體下周一火化　港澳將下半旗 （屌臭李鵬老母）","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:19.000Z","uid":56682,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f19f5f72a010124b2f3bd30e2f9c2a8559e380d","tid":1373461,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"在1989年六四期間對學生態度強硬的原國務院總理李鵬周一（22日）逝世，其遺體將於下周一（29日）在北京火化，當日上午在八寶山革命公墓將舉行高級別的告別儀式，屆時首都天安門、新華門、人民大會堂、外交部，各省、自治區、直轄市黨委和政府所在地，香港特別行政區、澳門特別行政區，各邊境口岸，對外海空港口，中國駐外使領館將下半旗致哀。<br />\n<br />\n來源：明報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老未，香港人開香檳慶祝呀！<br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要集體做D嘢，唔係全世界都覺得香港人支持李鵬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有咩計？"},{"pid":"f3ef438911d39b2d6572642df86120a46b650f1a","tid":1373461,"uid":199134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"每人揸住支香港旗慶祝"},{"pid":"f76f4281ba3fe951ef7653a5af5ec4599cb30c31","tid":1373461,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"581331a33abfdd5f787a7b9918264d6de26971f9","tid":1373461,"uid":274655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"聽日出去嘉年華同慶賀"},{"pid":"002035aab77a2bbb3bf6da33a7bc05b36b48c0ad","tid":1373461,"uid":56682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"全城嘉年華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbeb89b9220d349bef5ba75ba0dd35057d41db1","tid":1373461,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"出去開香賓?"}]}